{"database_schema": ""Description for table: Withdraw"
type Withdraw implements Event @entity(immutable: true) @transaction {
  "Unique identifier for the withdraw event"
  id: Bytes!
  "Transaction hash associated with the withdraw event"
  hash: Bytes!
  "Nonce value used in the transaction"
  nonce: BigInt!
  "Index of the log entry in the block"
  logIndex: Int!
  "Price of gas at the time of the transaction"
  gasPrice: BigInt
  "Amount of gas used by the transaction"
  gasUsed: BigInt
  "Maximum amount of gas allowed for the transaction"
  gasLimit: BigInt
  "Block number in which the transaction was included"
  blockNumber: BigInt!
  "Timestamp of when the transaction was mined"
  timestamp: BigInt!
  "Account involved in the withdraw event"
  account: Account!
  "Actor associated with the account, if any"
  accountActor: Account
  "Market related to the withdraw event"
  market: Market!
  "Position associated with the withdraw event"
  position: Position!
  "Token asset involved in the withdraw event"
  asset: Token!
  "Amount of the asset withdrawn"
  amount: BigInt!
  "USD equivalent of the withdrawn amount"
  amountUSD: BigDecimal!
}"}
